sections.heading: commissioner; city council member and mayor ineligible
sections.text: No member of the city council or the mayor of a city of the first class shall be eligible to the office of water commissioner during the term for which he or she shall be elected.SourceLaws 1901, c. 18, ยง 64, p. 278;R.S.1913, ยง 4964;C.S.1922, ยง
